    <div id="about" class="col-md-9" style="text-align:justify">
        <p>I am a Ph.D. candidate at <a href="https://www.ulaval.ca/">Université Laval</a> with Prof. <a
                href="https://www2.ift.ulaval.ca/~chaib/"> Brahim Chaib-Draa </a> and Prof. <a
                href="https://sites.google.com/site/borriewang/home?authuser=0"> Boyu Wang </a> in  <a href="https://www.uwo.ca/"> Western University</a>.
            Prior to my Ph.D. program, I was working on vehicle engineering especially on electrical vehicles control 
            supervised by <a
                href="http://shi.buaa.edu.cn/09007/zh_CN/index.htm"> Prof.Shichuang Yang </a> and <a
            href="http://shi.buaa.edu.cn/07312/zh_CN/index.htm"> Prof. Bin Xu </a> in Beihang University. </p>
            
            
        <p>My research areas includes transfer learning, domain adaptation and multi-task learning.
        </p>
        <p>Contact: fan.zhou.1[at]ulaval.ca
        </p>
    </div>


